text: Florida is a city and commune in Chile with 10067 inhabitants and an area of 609 square kilometres, all according to the census on 2002. The city is located at 42 kilometres to the eastern of Concepción. == History == The city was founded on 1755 by Antonio de Seravia. == References == == Other websites == * Municipality of the city of Florida (Chile) Category:Cities in Chile Category:Concepción Province, Chile
title: Florida, Chile
